PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Natural Resources of DOUGLAS W. THOMPSON of Victoria, British Columbia, as a director of Atomic Energy of Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Hugh Robert Wynne-Edwards, whose term has expired.
